title: This New Fifty Shades Darker Trailer Is Pure Steam
text:
This New Fifty Shades Darker Trailer Is Pure Steam 
Hello, Jamie Dornan's six-pack. By Alyssa Bailey Jan 8, 2017 Allow this new Fifty Shades Darker trailer—featuring many gratuitous shots of Jamie Dornan's Christian Grey working out shirtless and making out with Anastasia Steele shirtless in the shower—to warm up your January. No more secrets. #FiftyShadesDarker , in theaters February 10. Tickets: https://t.co/y1oI1Sb48Z pic.twitter.com/AwSz3e3iCD 
— Fifty Shades Darker (@FiftyShades) January 8, 2017 Advertisement - Continue Reading Below
